          "name": "decimals",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "Indicator of whether the oracle gets the data from or out of the `Stellar` ledger.\\nOracles that have this set to `true` will receive a request with [`Asset::Stellar`] asset\\nparameter first, and only if it returns [`None`] will receive [`Asset::Other`] afterwards.\\nThe opposite behavior takes place otherwise",
          "name": "is_stellar_data_based",
          "type_": "bool"
        },
        {
          "doc": "Default tick period timeframe",
          "name": "resolution",
          "type_": "u32"
